# 🤖 AI Chatbot with Conversation Memory

A full‑stack AI chatbot built with **Spring Boot (Spring AI)** and **React (CDN)**.  
It remembers your name and conversation context using Spring AI’s `MessageChatMemoryAdvisor`.

## ✨ Features
- **Real AI responses** – powered by OpenAI GPT (configurable)
- **Conversation memory** – remembers what you said across turns
- **Clean chat UI** – React frontend with typing indicator
- **Production‑ready backend** – Spring Boot REST API with CORS support

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Java 17, Spring Boot 3.2, Spring AI (OpenAI starter)
- **Frontend**: React 18 (via CDN), CSS
- **Build Tool**: Maven

## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Java 17+
- Maven (or use the included Maven wrapper)
- OpenAI API key (get one from [OpenAI Platform](https://platform.openai.com/api-keys))

### Run the backend
```bash
cd backend
export OPENAI_API_KEY=your-key-here   # Linux/macOS
# or set OPENAI_API_KEY=your-key-here (Windows)
./mvnw spring-boot:run